data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom home in Kiln Creek offers a spacious and comfortable living space. The open floor plan features a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and breakfast area. The master bedroom includes walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub. This home offers many upgrades beautiful mantle piece and built in bookcases. Outside, is a lovely backyard for relaxing and entertaining. Located in the desirable Kiln Creek community, this home is close to shopping, dining and entertainment options. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this your dream home.
